To calculate Graycode(n), we basically need to prefix 0 to each number GrayCode(n-1), prefix 1 to each number in reversed GrayCode(n-1), and add them up. 

Prefixing 1 can be done by adding 2^(n-1).

Example GrayCode(2) to GrayCode(3) :
0 00
0 01
0 11
0 10
1 10
1 11
1 01
1 00

