        List<Integer> code = new ArrayList<>();

        // i-th code sequence of the graycode
        for (int i = 0; i < 1 << n; i++) {
            code.add(i ^ (i >> 1));
        }

        return code;
    }
}
```
**Complexity Analysis**
Time complexity: O(2^n)
Space complexity: O(1)

