##### Example:- 1 2 3 4 5 6 7; k = 4; n = 7
1. Reverse the k elements from the last:
<pre>reverse(nums.end() - k, nums.end());      // 1 2 3 7 6 5 4</pre>
2. Then reverse the elements form index 0 to n-k-1:
<pre>reverse(nums.begin(), nums.end() - k);    // 3 2 1 7 6 5 4</pre>
3. Now reverse the whole nums;
<pre>reverse(nums.begin(), nums.end());        // 4 5 6 7 1 2 3</pre> 


